{"tid":1691837,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】五毛退散 光復連登 善用不推文瘋狂quote","createTime":"2019-11-03T22:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T03:30:49.000Z","uid":279356,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9845d855fda9bb74681d49e92e2fde2f88e0f81a","tid":1691837,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T22:08:19.000Z","msg":"善用檢舉功能 : 作用好似不大,要集氣report先優先處理卦我估<br />\n善用追故模式 : 以免死錯人<br />\n善用起底功能 : 同上 不廢話 你懂的<br />\n<br />\n重點 &darr;  &darr;  &darr; <br />\n善用不推文瘋狂quote :<br />\n不論五毛藍共畜是咪頭版留cm<br />\n理應<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">重點引用轉推</span></strong><br />\n務求令<span style=\"color: orange;\">該留言</span>望落達到一定關注度<br />\n舉個例子 &darr; <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1690240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1690240</a> <br />\n#8 我已經quote到5百幾,目標一千<br />\n(唔知最盡去到幾多)<br />\n我叫佢道歉並唔係真係想佢道歉<br />\n而係當時我人在街上求其打quote住先<br />\n當有過百過千人去quote<br />\n而幾乎清一色既留言要求該用戶被禁言<br />\n咁仲係唔係admin一方既一言堂?<br />\n其實同檢舉功能相似<br />\n但引用係公開用戶名稱<br />\n比起就咁負皮透明度高好多<br />\n我成日覺得admin唔落實點評開名功能<br />\n或<br />\n唔禁6月打後ac係可能驚比人覺得一言堂<br />\n我知佢之前回應過<br />\n但我睇唔明 TLDR 唔理lu<br />\n所以我地要助攻<br />\n自動波民意(引用功能)是可貴的<br />\n可能你會擔心對手係咁買ac hack ac<br />\n做同一樣野擾亂視聽<br />\n尋日仲見到有人話自己ac被自動登出<br />\n所以大家都要改左pw先<br />\n<br />\n落實去做既有三個步驟<br />\n1. 檢舉左先,填一d你認為合適既原因等admin判斷<br />\n2. 引用留言打「強烈要求admin將你禁言」直截了當<br />\n3. 當引用達一千(我set高d係因為過千點都會係民意卦?)<br />\n你可以自動波去站務區出po講聲<br />\n最好有重覆po添<br />\n<br />\n如果樓主唔想收到通知<br />\n咁你關掉通知就是了<br />\n大家<br />\n你地係有心限制畜生留言就唔好怕煩<br />\n共同承擔責任,打多幾隻字唔會晒你好多時間<br />\n可行嗎? 討論下"},{"pid":"ebd77fa178a79a4a72575a322aa639fbde00ab91","tid":1691837,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T22:10:19.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"795899a2c1ae998c94be93755dbf29d5b569eea1","tid":1691837,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebd77fa178a79a4a72575a322aa639fbde00ab91","tid":1691837,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T22:10:19.000Z","msg":"agger"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T22:35:29.000Z","msg":"作為P,無懼比人串都要留句<br />\n「強烈要求admin將你禁言」<br />\n比起就咁點評更屬民意<br />\n當然最好加自己見解,減低風向L作崇"},{"pid":"10a33a9955f46001db164d7958dcef2b3f7c0db6","tid":1691837,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:31:27.000Z","msg":"係咪覺得係廢、無用 <br />\n好似罷工一樣<br />\n跟住唔響應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0458021daf13c69da70b242cfd131e6b349729e6","tid":1691837,"uid":241742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:10:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11399fb9d48f48477144618cc87399b48897afb","tid":1691837,"uid":241742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6c97cd13952b71b6750c57983e8e324fcdd2fa","tid":1691837,"uid":241742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:10:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1676677e679e72931c3ab3472346a94a0a717953","tid":1691837,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f6c97cd13952b71b6750c57983e8e324fcdd2fa","tid":1691837,"uid":241742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:10:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:19:0